{"tid":2009041,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)地底精蟲1-2 鬼鏡 極速激戰","createTime":"2020-05-09T12:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T20:00:31.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"68811080052975383d8fee75153df8fb7a725d63","tid":2009041,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=012e131f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=97115e86\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=fa2a451b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/33/Tremorsposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F33%2FTremorsposter.jpg&h=b3b49847&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.gtimg.cn/qqlive/img/jpgcache/files/qqvideo/5/52ky50j9v4tzcjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.gtimg.cn%2Fqqlive%2Fimg%2Fjpgcache%2Ffiles%2Fqqvideo%2F5%2F52ky50j9v4tzcjp.jpg&h=08ba16d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/e3/Need_For_Speed_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fe%2Fe3%2FNeed_For_Speed_poster.jpg&h=57135f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1凱文貝肯&ldquo;野東西&rdquo;與佛瑞德華德是內華達州一個叫做&ldquo;完美鎮&rdquo;上的臨時工人，正當他們準備離開這個荒涼小鎮，到別處求發展時，卻發現當地居民與家畜神秘死亡的屍體，死因皆離奇怪異、不合邏輯。不久後他們赫然發現，兇手並不是什麼殺人犯，而是比殺人犯殘忍幾百倍的上千隻巨形突變怪蟲！它們潛伏在地底下，然後以迅雷不及掩耳的動作從地心竄出，吞噬地面上的人類與家畜！此時，小鎮居民陷入了恐慌之中&hellip;&hellip;他們兩人是否能幫助小鎮居民，打擊地心怪物呢？系列影片共五部<br />\n<br />\n2.在《異形魔怪》第一集中逃過蟲吻的硬漢厄爾（佛瑞德華德）與柏特（麥可葛羅斯）再次攜手合作，加上美麗的地質學家（海倫薛佛） ，三人一起對抗這只邪惡的地心怪物，好將它們永遠消滅，然而這只噁心的怪獸竟然變成了用紅外線探測人體體溫的新型怪物&mdash;&mdash;尖叫獸，他們最後能把它​​​​們消滅嗎？<br />\n<br />\n3.班卡森（基佛蘇德蘭飾）曾經是個出色的紐約警探，卻在一次出勤時誤殺臥底的同伴，感到愧疚不已的他，漸漸沈迷於酒精之中，酗酒和暴怒的脾氣，讓他與親人的關係日漸疏遠，最後只能借住在妹妹家，睡在沙發上。<br />\n因緣際會下，卡森來到已成廢墟的五月花百貨擔任保全，這個曾經一度是奢華與雄偉象徵的百貨公司，因為一場大火而沒落，大火吞噬了整棟建築，許多無辜的生命喪生於此。五年過去，在各種官司與產權問題沒有著落下，這棟焦黑的建築只任放置著任由它傾倒..<br />\n<br />\n4.托比&middot;馬歇爾是一位普通的改裝車行的修車工，他在紐約基斯科山的車庫時常與好友們改裝車輛。某日，托比昔日的仇人蒂諾&middot;布魯斯特開著一輛梅賽德斯-奔馳SLR McLaren來到托比的車庫，要約他完成賽車手卡羅&middot;謝爾比生前未完成建造的福特謝爾比野馬[5]。迪諾要托比和他的隊友完成該項目，以換取汽車200萬元的估計售價中25%。儘管隊友們都反對，但托比還是同意了<br />\n<br />\n8 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e4ff5e13\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https: